* Content:
============

Folder contains a program that simulates the mutual exclusion problem using system V semaphore.

    Included files:    
    1) main.c					main program

    2) lib_sem.h					semaphore functions
       lib_sem.c					library 
------------------------------------------------------------------------

* How to run:
=========================

Catalog contains Makefile for compiling and running the program.

-> To compile, type make
-> To run the program, type make run
-> For after-usage-clean, type make clean
========================================================================







